|CKBConfuse: Certainty Applied Incorrectly|000

Syntax: confuse [foe]

Point out the ambush that is not there. Correct your foe's stance with great
authority. Ask whether they remembered to lock the door. For a few precious
moments, the mark may be too tangled in your certainty to act properly.

Confuse is available from Charlatan Rank 1. Misdirection makes the lie easier
to sell, keeps it alive longer, and makes it less exhausting. The cloak will
never stake more than 150 SP on one story. Confuse takes longer to recover than
the distraction lasts. Success tells you when Sucker Punch is primed. A foe
who sees through you still costs the effort and recovery time; embarrassment
is not a refund policy.
